transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra at Score Blue. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: With Nick.

Speaker 1: Hello.

Speaker 2: Hello, is this Nick?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir. Hello. Hi, who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today? This is Brian Boone.

Speaker 2: Hi, Mr. Boone, how can I help you?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I sent back those three bottles like you told me.

Speaker 2: Uh-huh.

Speaker 1: And—

Speaker 2: I did get a refund of 63.95.

Speaker 1: But that was just for one bottle.

Speaker 2: So I'm looking at your account right now, Mr. Boone.

Speaker 1: I'm not sure about what the delay was, but we have issued three refunds of 63.95.

Speaker 2: Okay, what were the dates on those? Those all three were refunded on the 21st?

Speaker 1: 21st.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yeah, all those refunds were—all those were refunded. I mean, you can reach out to your bank.

Speaker 2: But I see every single one was refunded, all three.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay, it's only showing up as one, so I have to check with them and see what's going on.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All three were on the 21st.

Speaker 1: Yes, sir, that's three of them for 63.95.

Speaker 2: Okay, I'll check with them then, all right.

Speaker 1: Okay, thank you. Uh, thank you.

Speaker 2: Have a good day.
